#BETTER LIFE RFs

• User Authentication and Access Control (roles for view, edit, and admin permissions)
• Commenting and Note-taking (commenting on specific parts of documents)
• Export and Print (export to PDF, Word, Excel; print documents)
• Offline Mode (ability to work offline and sync later)
• Templates (pre-designed templates for common documents like reports, resumes, etc.)
• Scheduling and Calendar (integrate and schedule meetings, reminders)
• File Sharing (share files with others via links or permissions)
• Task Management (to-do list, assigning tasks to others, classification of tasks, proyects with tasks inside...)

